WEBVTT

00:00.016 --> 00:01.635
<i>Previously on "Damien"...</i>

00:01.636 --> 00:03.265
[Tires screech]

00:04.352 --> 00:06.021
Help!

00:06.022 --> 00:07.640
I blame you for those deaths,

00:07.664 --> 00:09.663
the evil you felt that night.

00:09.664 --> 00:10.913
[Window shatters, women scream]

00:10.914 --> 00:12.493
ANN: It comes from inside of you.

00:12.494 --> 00:14.623
You showed him the shrine?
How did he take it?

00:14.624 --> 00:15.546
He'll be back.

00:15.571 --> 00:16.882
That's three dead by freak accident.

00:16.907 --> 00:17.765
It's a holy trinity.

00:17.813 --> 00:18.812
It's Kelly's notebook.

00:18.813 --> 00:20.874
She must've been working on
some kind of religious story.

00:20.898 --> 00:23.057
[Dog barks and snarls]

00:23.058 --> 00:24.477
[Gunshot, dog whimpers]

00:24.734 --> 00:26.813
We've been thinking
it's time for a change.

00:26.814 --> 00:28.353
Troy will take over.

00:28.354 --> 00:30.613
ANN: There are very
mysterious forces at work.

00:30.614 --> 00:32.313
They can't be manipulated.

00:32.314 --> 00:35.314
They operate according to design.

00:38.444 --> 00:41.654
[Fizzing]

00:43.000 --> 00:49.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:50.524 --> 00:53.314
[Water trickling]

00:56.404 --> 00:58.654
[Water splashing]

01:07.614 --> 01:09.814
[Exhales deeply]

01:12.484 --> 01:15.773
[Water dripping]

01:15.774 --> 01:17.814
<i>[Thud]</i>

01:20.274 --> 01:23.154
[Gasps]

01:26.854 --> 01:29.314
[Knobs squeak]

01:32.944 --> 01:34.654
[Sighs]

01:41.694 --> 01:42.854
[Water dripping]

01:46.564 --> 01:48.314
<i>[Thud]</i>

01:56.194 --> 01:59.314
[Water draining]

02:02.654 --> 02:04.484
[Whispers] Jesus.

02:07.314 --> 02:09.312
[Squish]

02:09.314 --> 02:13.313
♪♪

02:13.314 --> 02:14.484
<i>[Roars]</i>

02:14.485 --> 02:15.654
[Screams]

02:16.654 --> 02:18.354
[Gasps]

02:23.444 --> 02:25.154
- [Water dripping]
- [Exhales]

02:32.814 --> 02:34.314
Ugh.

02:37.444 --> 02:40.813
[Gurgles, bubbles]

02:40.814 --> 02:42.404
[Inhales sharply]

02:43.564 --> 02:47.314
♪♪

02:51.314 --> 02:55.154
♪♪

